Author: Butty43
Text: You won't gain any permanent weight from that if it was a one off. Maybe a little water weight that will be gone in a day or 2. No worries. And it will help speed up your metabolism.

Author: fishonthesun
Text: Don't panic! Don't stress! I don't want to mention toooooo specific of numbers but at most you're looking at 1/4 lb true weight gain. Anything more than that is just water weight, food weight, or perhaps hormones.  Added bonus, when you eat more food, you burn more cals in the digestive process. Not a ton more, but there is that little silver lining too (-:
